    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/353d688864a8b5730b3d42c7a7abf25c.avif?t=1767933656\" width=612 height=137 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the Institute Of Skam!</h2><br>You are Boris, the newest employee of a scam call center in Plövka, a tiny Eastern European dictatorship.<br><br>Newly emerged from isolation, Plövkans must find new ways to make money, but are<br>clueless about the modern world. Overcome your ignorance to cleverly deceive<br>Westerners, using a range of scams. Bask in the glory of your grateful nation, earn a few kropeks, and avoid being fired (and returning to your former job in the fluoride mines).<br><br>Good luck, patriot!<br><br>                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/7ddd4547eecdbc6bf2c6e218e95ca3bb.poster.avif?t=1767933656\" width=430 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/7ddd4547eecdbc6bf2c6e218e95ca3bb.webm?t=1767933656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/7ddd4547eecdbc6bf2c6e218e95ca3bb.mp4?t=1767933656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/9132a72f98b3cf80703d3642dc22e73a.avif?t=1767933656\" width=617 height=73 /></span><br><br>                    * Make calls and steer the scam towards a successful ending. <br>                    * Navigate dialogue options ranging from friendly to furious.<br>                    * Different targets might be chatty, nervous or belligerent <br>                       (and everything in between). <br>                    * Base your dialogue choices on the targets' personalities and moods.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/2bacf42f32c9b808d9d372c320f968c4.avif?t=1767933656\" width=617 height=73 /></span><br><br>                    * Talk to plenty of different callers, all with distinctive personas. <br>                    * Every line of caller dialogue is fully voiced.<br><br>                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/d0817349b47dcf8a1fff8c4222d9d9c8.poster.avif?t=1767933656\" width=430 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/d0817349b47dcf8a1fff8c4222d9d9c8.webm?t=1767933656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/d0817349b47dcf8a1fff8c4222d9d9c8.mp4?t=1767933656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/c483d24f0c5b8a16c7b18d5d9939fb77.avif?t=1767933656\" width=617 height=73 /></span><br><br>                    * You have a short fuse. Manage your irritation, or it will boil over into rage, <br>                       causing you to explode during promising calls and ruin them. <br>                    * Find ways to manage stress between calls. <br>                    * Lower stress during calls by yelling at trolls and timewasters.<br><br>                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/79c14b15e9b098b67fbe4c58190a110a.poster.avif?t=1767933656\" width=430 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/79c14b15e9b098b67fbe4c58190a110a.webm?t=1767933656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/79c14b15e9b098b67fbe4c58190a110a.mp4?t=1767933656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/f1625f2cbb6b00d9618d1d457b838eb7.avif?t=1767933656\" width=617 height=73 /></span><br><br>                    * Unlock new and increasingly diabolical scams. <br>                    * Each one works on a different type of target, so you’ll have to master them all.<br>                    * Use your Book of Skam to guide you through tricky calls.<br><br>                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/8afd853f0aef572eb4ecf1f2f207e51d.poster.avif?t=1767933656\" width=430 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/8afd853f0aef572eb4ecf1f2f207e51d.webm?t=1767933656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/8afd853f0aef572eb4ecf1f2f207e51d.mp4?t=1767933656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081160/extras/9404aab6c7ffa12f37aaee377737ca59.avif?t=1767933656\" width=617 height=73 /></span><br><br>                    * New skills and knowledge will help you in your dubious quest. <br>                    * Improv classes, fake accents, and pop culture knowledge <br>                       will all lead to Skam Glory.",
